Today, let me share with you a day in my life, in Boracay! 💙🌊

There are lots of delish restos here in Boracay that’s why its so hard for me to eat healthy. Im so glad I have my fav Arla Natural Yogurt. Its the best snack ever!! 

Im mixing my Arla yogurt with some granola now but usually I just eat it as is. It’s all-natural, no artificial colors, & all natural fruity flavors😍 plus it’s light and fat-free

Eating good food really does make a difference. It gives us more energy throughout the day making me enjoy my beach activities even more.

Anyway, it’s time for me to get ready for tomorrow, catch you later!
